<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Freeman_Dyson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=21" title="Edit section: Bibliography">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Bibliography</span></h2>
<p><a name="By_Dyson" id="By_Dyson"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Freeman_Dyson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: By Dyson">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">By Dyson</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><i>Symmetry Groups in Nuclear and Particle Physics</i>, 1966 (Academic-oriented text)</li>
<li><i>Disturbing the Universe</i>, 1979. <a href="http://adsabs.harvard.edu/full/1983IrAJ...16...88D" class="external text" title="http://adsabs.harvard.edu/full/1983IrAJ...16...88D" rel="nofollow">Review</a></li>
<li><i>Weapons and Hope</i>, 1984 (Winner of the National Book Critics Circle Award).<sup id="cite_ref-civil_3-5" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-civil-3" title=""><span>[</span>4<span>]</span></a></sup> <a href="http://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/38538/andrew-j-pierre/weapons-and-hope" class="external text" title="http://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/38538/andrew-j-pierre/weapons-and-hope" rel="nofollow">Review</a></li>
<li><i>Origins of Life</i>, 1986. Second edition, 1999. <a href="http://www.complete-review.com/reviews/dysonf/origins.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.complete-review.com/reviews/dysonf/origins.htm" rel="nofollow">Review</a></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Infinite_in_All_Directions" title="Infinite in All Directions">Infinite in All Directions</a></i>, 1988. <a href="http://www.cs.sfu.ca/~anoop/weblog/archives/000161.html" class="external text" title="http://www.cs.sfu.ca/~anoop/weblog/archives/000161.html" rel="nofollow">Review</a></li>
<li><i>From Eros to Gaia</i>, 1992</li>
<li><i>Selected Papers of Freeman Dyson</i>, 1996</li>
